ur study provides evidence that \"in-situ\" massive clump formation\n(as also observed at high redshifts) is very efficiently induced by large-scale\ninstabilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2023 08:39:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-27"}
